== About ==

MysqlLikeSearch is an extension of the MediaWiki.
This extension implements a like search instead of the index search.


For more information:
  * https://github.com/uta/MysqlLikeSearch



== Requirement ==

MediaWiki 1.24+



== Download ==

You can get the code directly from Git.

$ git clone https://github.com/uta/MysqlLikeSearch.git



== Installation ==

Once you have downloaded the code, place the ''MysqlLikeSearch'' directory
to extensions directory of your MediaWiki.

Then add the following code to your LocalSettings.php:

require_once( "$IP/extensions/MysqlLikeSearch/MysqlLikeSearch.php" );
